<bold><italic>reatment: </italic></bold>The NYHA classification, LVESD, LVEDD, LVEF and 6-minutes walking distance of the two groups after treatment were significantly better than those before (P&#x0003c;0.05). In the meantime, the indices of the observation group significantly exceeded those of the control group after treatment (P&#x0003c;0.05) (<xref ref-type="table" rid="T2">Table-II</xref>, <xref ref-type="fig" rid="F1">Fig. 1</xref>-<xref ref-type="fig" rid="F3">3</xref>).</p><p>
